Ad blocker enabled
An ad blocker is enabled in your browser. Please note that not all contents of the site can potentially be displayed correctly depending on the ad blocker settings.
We take the protection of personal data extremely seriously. We provide our internet website in compliance with the applicable legal regulations for the protection of personal data (especially the General Data Protection Regulation / GDPR). With this data protection information we provide you as the user with information about how we deal with personal data collected in the course of your visit to our portal.
This data protection information applies exclusively to the portal provided by SMP GmbH & Co. KG (further, "SMP"). The portal may contain links to other third-party websites to which this data protection information does not apply. If you leave our portal we recommend that you read carefully other websites' data protection information
